    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8058-9ac5-dc12bc520b9f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Moreover, the paper delves into how these analytics are used at an institutional level (often they aren’t) and discusses possible reasons for this. ",
